        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2288679936" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13014356163848564743">Brent Weeks packs lots of content into &apos;&apos;Shadow’s Edge&apos;&apos; and as with the first novel in the series there are lots of different story strands which tie together nicely, although a few are left open for the final book.<br/><br/>This is a great book and I found it to be well written, with some strong characters and I look forward to reading the final novel in the series soon.</span>
  <span id="freeText13014356163848564743" style="display:none">Brent Weeks packs lots of content into ''Shadow’s Edge'' and as with the first novel in the series there are lots of different story strands which tie together nicely, although a few are left open for the final book.<br /><br />This is a great book and I found it to be well written, with some strong characters and I look forward to reading the final novel in the series soon.</span>
