<li class='cover' id='bookCover_6736971'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6736971-the-desert-spear"><img alt="The Desert Spear (Demon Cycle, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388219761l/6736971._SX98_.jpg" />
